name: Prime-Line Torsion Spring Cable Drum - Die-Cast 1/8 in.
description: This torsion spring cable drum is constructed from diecast. It accepts cables up to 1/8 in. in diameter with a maximum weight load of 265 lbs. per drum. This drum spools your lifting cable as your garage door is operated.Die-cast constructionUsed on torsion spring garage doorsAccepts cables up to 1/8 in. in diameterMaximum weight load of 265 lbs. per drumHanding is determined by standing inside the garage looking outward
